{"tid":1520061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見巴打都話罷食牛陣！我忍唔撚住啦","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:00:30.000Z","uid":288018,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff950e952716c67bb362984fcc1b87f5a34ab87","tid":1520061,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"早排我同朋友去旺角食牛陣<br />\n入到去無乜人，我地講野唔算大聲。正常聲量<br />\n我地係到講到 黑警還眼單野<br />\n樓面個員工就好似聽到我地講緊啲咩⋯⋯啤左我地一下..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,我地再講佢又再啤。我地最後未夠鐘就走。再食都唔知會唔會啲野食比人加左野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">岩見到巴打講完我都忍唔撚住</span></span></strong><br />\n係深藍深撚到咁啊。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁巴閉，唔比客人講野</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你就唔好開門/寫明不招呼深黃</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷食牛陣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可恥</span></span>"},{"pid":"ab285230a505aa57e55a0b513fcf5b88982b4069","tid":1520061,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2bP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=baf676fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpM